Flatdango

Flatdango is a mini movie ticket booking application that allows users to view movies, check available tickets, and buy tickets for shows.

Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- JSON Server

Setup
1. Clone the repository.
2. Run npm install -g json-server if JSON Server is not installed.
3. Start the JSON server using json-server --watch db.json.
4. Open index.html in your browser.

Features
- View movie details
- Check available tickets
- Purchase tickets

 Bonus Features
- Movies are marked as sold out when no tickets are available.